OL,6,CStage A
OL,8,GProtests and marches. Graduates booing
OL,9,Gcommencement speakers. Self-driving
OL,10,Gcars set on fire. Why are people so
OL,11,Gangry about AI? Well, plenty of
OL,12,Greasons, and some of them very
OL,13,Gobvious, but why is there pushback
OL,14,Gright now and how is it happening? It
OL,15,Gso happens we've just run a survey on
OL,16,Gexactly that, and we have some answers
OL,17,G– and more questions. Like: what is
OL,18,Gthe future for a technology that an
OL,19,Gincreasing number of people love to
OL,20,Ghate?
